[h2 id=WhatisFDS? 
	" What is FDS?
	$LF
]h2
[p 
	"FDS is Famicom Disk System.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"It's a special Famicom-like (Famicom is the Japanese
	$LF
	"name of Nintendo Entertainment System) console where
	$LF
	"games are loaded from diskettes.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"FDS images are different from NES images in that they
	$LF
	"are usually named 
	[tt 
		".fds
	]tt
	", not 
	[tt 
		".nes
	]tt
	",
	$LF
	"and that you also need a disk system BIOS image
	$LF
	"(usually named as 
	[tt 
		"disksys.rom
	]tt
	" for emulators).
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Do not ask us (the author of this site or the people at
	$LF
	"the nesvideos forum) to send you ROMs or FDS images.
	$LF
	"Any such messages will be deleted.
]p
